OL,6,FVideo report by ITV Granada Reports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Rob Smith
OL,9,F, has been jailed for a minimum of 19
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FIan Connell, 39, strangled Donald
OL,13,F'Prentice' Patience, 45, in a "fit of
OL,14,Frage" after his victim refused to give
OL,15,Fhim more money to feed his heroin and
OL,16,Fcrack cocaine habit.
