OL,6,FThe decomposing body of Mr Patience,
OL,7,Fwas discovered inside a duvet cover at
OL,8,Fthe bottom of his stairs after police
OL,9,Fwere called to reports of a burglary
OL,10,Fat his home in , Greater Manchester.
OL,12,FA postman dialled 999 on the morning
OL,13,Fof August 22 last year when he saw a
OL,14,Fman climb through the rear kitchen
OL,15,Fwindow of the end terrace property in
OL,16,FAinsworth Road.
OL,18,FWhen police arrived soon afterwards,
OL,19,FConnell was nearby with Mr Patience's
OL,20,Fwhite labradoodle, Layla, on a lead.
