OL,6,FHe said the defendant used Mr Patience
OL,7,Fas an "open wallet" in receiving
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds since they first
OL,9,Fmet.
OL,11,FMr Patience's sister-in-law gave a
OL,12,Fstatement to the court calling him
OL,13,F"one of the kindest and most generous
OL,14,Fpeople." She added there's "a void
OL,15,Fwithin the family that will never be
OL,16,Ffilled" and telling his children of
OL,17,Fhis death was a "conversation you
OL,18,Fshould never have to have."
