OL,7,Ftold Connell he'd shown a "temper"
OL,8,Fduring the trial who shook his head
OL,9,Fand snorted during sentencing.
OL,11,FAs he was taken away to start a life
OL,12,Fterm, that won't allow for parole for
OL,13,F19 years, he said swearing: "It wasn't
OL,14,Fme, your honour. I didn't do it. End
OL,15,Fof conversation."
